    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next adventure! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, it\u2019s super reliable and runs like a dream. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a fantastic vehicle that's ready to hit the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love it!",
