    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This driver-focused machine delivers a raw, visceral experience with its high-revving naturally aspirated engine and close-ratio manual gearbox. The powertrain remains robust, exhibiting excellent compression across all cylinders and a crisp throttle response. Mechanically sound with a recently serviced limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension bushings, it maintains sharp turn-in and neutral handling characteristics. While the aesthetics show honest signs of use consistent with its history, the chassis rigidity and drivetrain alignment are superb. Perfect for the enthusiast seeking a mechanically sorted platform that prioritizes power-to-weight efficiency and analog feedback over showroom cosmetics.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
