    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior finish retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the minor character marks and light stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system\u2014function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, benefited by a documented history of on-time oil changes and a recent brake service. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the tires have approximately 75% tread remaining. It is a solid, honest car that drives tight and offers the peace of mind that comes from a history of responsible ownership.",
